Looking back on 2023 I'm really proud of what I was able to accomplish despite a good share of setbacks and burnout struggles. I cosplayed 11 new characters plus 4 more completely hand made cosplays that were passion projects for me! (Bloomlordmon, Aphrodite, Crysta and Jinx). Aside from cosplay, streaming has been a super big part of my year. I finished setting up my stream room and finally made the leap back into twitch in 2023 and couldn't be more thankful for my amazing community giving me the warmest welcome back. I've streamed some games that are now among my all time favourites including RE4 remake and BG3! And of course, hitting partner was a special milestone to me and I'm very thankful I have such an awesome community supporting me. I'm so grateful for the time I got to spend with my loved ones and the amazing souls around me for giving me the gift of their friendship. I'm looking forward to making some new cosplays in 2024, continuing my streaming journey and making more memories with my people 💖
